@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.53)
    v0 = ((v2 + wp.sin(v2 + 0.40)) - ((v1 + 0.32 / tmp + 0.81) / (v2 + 0.18 - v0 + 0.70)))
    v2 = 0.02
    v2 = wp.abs((0.39 * (tmp + 0.34 / tmp + 1.00)))
    v0 = 0.12
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
